{"tid":754410,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"舊愛遭網上欺凌 陳家樂留言安慰余香凝","createTime":"2018-07-24T11:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T04:01:15.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b3cfb18e952a00f67907c02a35a12cab8ad819","tid":754410,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"湯怡、陳家樂、吳浩康出席電影《廉政風雲 煙幕》煞科宴，在戲中扮演ICAC人員兼劉青雲得力助手的陳家樂，直言等待跟對方合作的機會很久，過往經常睇對方的電影，更視青雲為學習對象，又指青雲在拍攝現場不會玩電話，只會躲在角落培養情緒，表現得沉默寡言，認為應跟對方學習。<br />\n<br />\n提到舊愛余香凝因分手一事受到網絡欺凌，陳家樂也有留言鼓勵對方，說：「網絡欺凌不應該，但我不可以做到太多，亦沒有能力去做，只能畀她一點鼓勵。」"},{"pid":"d4951959e94e8e284ab50699f6f87fbcec66c491","tid":754410,"uid":37941,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"男人老狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩個都閪"},{"pid":"932682adcc3d8db1f2837b1a16e2765cf3a73024","tid":754410,"uid":130901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"強迫口爆，再善心遞紙巾"},{"pid":"d16f0ca2f2beaf8493ddb2eaa6aef7ce00e7567a","tid":754410,"uid":132405,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:40:26.000Z","msg":"明明之前先係ig出post欺凌完人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/194018_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F194018_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=61dfda43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e3d52d9de6ac67f74954ebb5bcff5b4fe4b46d5","tid":754410,"uid":21423,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc51b2d2119191f98b983097dfede5e935efa382","tid":754410,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"之後世紀復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/no